Default module in [[Node js]] at the moment of writing is [[Common js modules]]. To enable features of [[Es modules]]:

* change the file extension to `.mjs`
* add to your [[package.json|Package json]] following line: `"type": "module"`
* use node command line argument `--input-type=module`